Eric,

Fronts on a 78 are reflector only.  You need a VOM(volt ohm meter) to 
check your tail light housing and bulb holder.  Is the ground for that 
side attached well?

Which? lights don't work, running light, stop lights, turn signal lights, 
backup lights???

